Bringing the whole family together to share a TV show is no easy task, so check out our guide to the best TV shows for families. With a million and one other distractions, plus the challenge of satisfying multiple ages and finding a show that won’t terrify smaller members of the family, while not boring the socks off older ones, is a mighty challenge. 

So we’ve split our guide into three sections, one for families with younger kids, one for 9+ and one for 12-years and over, plus we’ve given the recommended age restriction so you can make your own informed choice about what is suitable for your brood.
